caption.title: Caspase-1 p20, IL-1β and IL-18 are elevated in the serum of MAYV-infected patients in comparison to healthy individuals.
caption.p: Serum samples of 13 MAYV-infected patients and 19 healthy control samples were included. Samples were diluted 1:2 for caspase-1 p20 ELISA (A), 1:5 for IL-1β ELISA (B) and 1:3 for IL-18 ELISA (C). Data are represented as scatterplots showing means ± SEM of samples. Statistical analysis was performed by student’s t test. Asterisks indicate significant differences ( P < 0.05) between MAYV-infected and control groups.
